  "original_title": "\u0ba8\u0bcb\u0bb0\u0bcd\u0bb5\u0bc2\u0b9f\u0bcd\u0b9f\u0bbf\u0bb2\u0bcd  \u0ba4\u0b99\u0bcd\u0b95\u0b95\u0bcd \u0b95\u0bc1\u0bb4\u0bbf",
  "text_idx": {
    "en": {
      "title": "Gold mine in Norwood",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Today, the police recovered one and a half kilo worth of gold worth around 3 crores 15 lakhs in the upper division of Venture Garden under Norwood police division and arrested four people in connection with the incident.",
        "This amount of gold was recovered during the joint search conducted by the Norwood Police and Crime Prevention Unit.",
        "On December 9, 2021, the owners of a jewelry store in Norwood complained to the Norwood Police Station that a large amount of jewelry had been stolen.",
        "Following this, a woman who had worked in the shop for about 10 years was arrested on suspicion and her fingerprints were recorded.",
        "The Norwood police and crime prevention unit, which has been conducting a series of investigations and searches for the past six months, has recovered the jewelery today and arrested four people, including a woman, on suspicion.",
        "The fingerprints of the woman who has already been arrested and interrogated are the same as those found in the recovered items, the police have said.",
        "Norwood police are conducting further investigations into the incident."
      ],
